    "Distance learning especially in computer science has seen a significant increase as educational institutions have shifted toward offering online courses.",
    "In the USA, 98% of universities have transitioned to online courses.",
    "Although some institutions quickly adapted, many struggled to modify traditional materials for online learners.",
    "Time was crucial for institutions lacking experience in remote teaching.",
    "Even before the shift, adult students (andragogical learners) preferred online programmes, and now, we anticipate a substantial increase in younger learners."
